TextEng: Well hello. I am <FullName>. Will you answer some questions?
Text: 안녕하세요. 저는 <FullName>입니다. 몇 가지 질문을 해도 될까요?

TextEng: I'm <FullName>. I have a few questions.
Text: 전 <FullName>입니다. 몇 가지 여쭤볼 게 있어요.

TextEng: I'm <FullName>. Just answer my questions.
Me <FullName>. Maybe me ask some questions?
Me <FullName>. You just answer questions and stop yappin'.
Text: 나 <FullName>. 말 많지 말고 질문에나 답해.

TextEng: Farewell for now.
Bye bye, okay?
What kind of place do you run here?
What kind of stuff happens here?
Know any rumors? Seen anything strange?
Text: 소문 좀 아세요? 이상한 걸 본 적은요?

TextEng: Maybe you knows things? Seen weird stuffs?
Text: 뭐 아는 거 있어? 이상한 거 봤어?

TextEng: You knows anything abouts the plague, maybe?
Have you heard anything about the plague?
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> You can trust me. What've you got to say?
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Trust me, okies? Yeah, 's all good.
I will get them. Give me more details.
Me help get art stuff. Know where they is?
Text: 나 그 예술품 가져와 줄게. 어디 있는지 알아?

TextEng: This does not interest me.
This is not my concern.
Tell me about these art objects.
So you want some pretty stuff? What is they?
Text: 예쁜 거 갖고 싶다는 거야? 뭐야 그게?

TextEng: No! Me demands more!
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> You must agree that I am worth more.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 제 값어치가 더 한다는 데 동의하시겠죠.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> You knows me worth more than that.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 내가 그보다 더 값진 거 알잖아.

TextEng: I demand more! Pay or prepare to suffer!
Text: 더 내놔! 아니면 대가를 치르게 될 거야!

TextEng: Me wants more, or me hurt you good!
Text: 더 줘, 아니면 혼쭐 내줄 거야!

TextEng: That is sufficient. Thank you.
That really good. Thanks for the stuff.
I don't care! I demand more!
<StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> And if they stopped, you might have to sell those secrets.
Text: <StartCheck>[통찰]</Start> 그게 끊기면, 당신도 그 비밀을 팔아야 할지도 모르겠군요.

TextEng: Come now, madam. Don't keep secrets between us.
Text: 자, 아가씨. 우리 사이에 비밀은 없도록 하죠.

TextEng: You pretty. Tell me stuff. No secrets.
Text: 예쁜 아가씨. 다 말해. 비밀 없게.

TextEng: I'm interested in the backroom.
Tell about backroom stuff for me. Yeah.
Don't play games. Tell me or shut the hell up.
Stupid word games! Just say or shut up!
Text: 바보 같은 말장난 그만! 말하든가 닥쳐!

TextEng: I want permission to access the backrooms.
Me wants in backroom place. Sounds fun.
A common bawdy house! I am outraged!
Bunch o' harlots and jigg-o-lers! You sick!
I already have a writ from him. Here.
Me gots it already. Uh, the paper, not plague.
Text: 나 벌써 받았어. 어, 종이 말야, 역병 말고.

TextEng: Thank you. I'll return directly.
Okies, me come back soon.
I have an art object you might be interested in.
Me gots art crap you might like.
Text: 좋아할 만한 예쁜 거 갖고 왔어.

TextEng: <StartAction>Describe securing the Statuette from Androd Golden.</Start>
Text: <StartAction>안드로드 골든에게서 작은 조각상을 확보한 경위를 설명합니다.</Start>

TextEng: <StartAction>Describe securing the Portrait from Thoms Rumbottom.</Start>
<StartAction>Describe securing the Urn from Hodge.</Start>
Nothing. Nevermind.
I have a writ from Oleff declaring me plague free.
Text: 올레프로부터 받은 역병 면제 증명서가 있습니다.

TextEng: Me gots Oleff to say me not sick! Here paper!
Text: 올레프가 나 안 아프다 했어! 여기 종이!

TextEng: This is nothing but a house of ill-repute!
This a dirty place! Filthy dirty!
What business do you need done?
You needs business or something done?
Text: 할 일 있어? 뭐 해 줄까?

TextEng: I've had enough. Goodbye!
Me not stay! Me leave!
